OL,3,CPort Talbot to become home of first
OL,4,Coffshore wind farm in Celtic Sea
OL,6,FPort Talbot will become home to the
OL,7,Ffirst offshore floating wind farm
OL,8,Fdeveloped in the Celtic Sea.
OL,10,FThe UK Government have announced a
OL,11,F#64m grant to allow Associated British
OL,12,FPorts (ABP) to design and engineer the
OL,13,Fhub.
OL,15,FThe port will support the development
OL,16,Fof 4.5GW of floating offshore wind
OL,17,Fprojects ` which are suited to the
OL,18,FCeltic Sea as they are based in deeper
OL,19,Fwaters where they can harness stronger
OL,20,Fand more consistent wind speeds `
OL,21,Fenough to power 6.5 million homes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
