PN,46502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774576986
OL,3,CPort Talbot to become home of first
OL,4,Coffshore wind farm in Celtic Sea
OL,6,FABP say they expect that once
OL,7,Fcompleted the new port will support
OL,8,Fthousands of jobs and unlock over
OL,9,F#500m in investment for Port Talbot.
OL,11,FThe plans form part of the
OL,12,Fgovernment's wider plans for clean
OL,13,Fenergy, with new housing rules
OL,14,Fmandating heat pumps and solar panels,
OL,15,Faccess to plug-in solar panels for
OL,16,Fhomeowners and bringing forward
OL,17,Frenewable energy auctions for major
OL,18,Fwind farms and other projects.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
