OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774576986
OL,3,CPort Talbot to become home of first
OL,4,Coffshore wind farm in Celtic Sea
OL,6,FThe announcement for Port Talbot comes
OL,7,Fas the UK faces rising energy costs as
OL,8,Fa result of the Middle East crisis,
OL,9,Fwhich has pushed up global oil and gas
OL,10,Fprices.
OL,12,FThere have been calls to increase
OL,13,Fdrilling in the North Sea in light of
OL,14,Fthe crisis following the US-Israeli
OL,15,Fwar on Iran, to boost energy security,
OL,16,Falthough experts have warned that will
OL,17,Fnot significantly bring down prices or
OL,18,Fsecure supplies.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
