CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774576986
OL,3,CPort Talbot to become home of first
OL,4,Coffshore wind farm in Celtic Sea
OL,6,FThe investment in Port Talbot comes
OL,7,Fafter uncertainty in the town
OL,8,Ffollowing TATA Steel's decision to
OL,9,Freplace the blast furnaces at the
OL,10,Fsite, affecting thousands of jobs.
OL,12,FWork to repurpose the site and build a
OL,13,Fnew Electric Arc Furnace (EAF) is
OL,14,Fongoing.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
