OL,3,CPort Talbot to become home of first
OL,4,Coffshore wind farm in Celtic Sea
OL,6,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband said:
OL,7,F"From floating offshore wind in Port
OL,8,FTalbot to a new generation of small
OL,9,Fmodular reactors at Wylfa ` this
OL,10,FGovernment is putting Wales at the
OL,11,Fheart of our clean energy superpower
OL,12,Fmission.
OL,14,F"With its deep waters and strong
OL,15,Fwinds, we are supporting to Wales to
OL,16,Fstorm ahead in floating offshore wind
OL,17,F` a pioneering industry that will
OL,18,Fsupport thousands of good jobs, drive
OL,19,Fgrowth across the country and unlock
OL,20,Fthe next generation of clean,
OL,21,Fhomegrown power."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@QO]
