CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774576986
OL,3,CPort Talbot to become home of first
OL,4,Coffshore wind farm in Celtic Sea
OL,6,FSecretary of State for Wales Jo
OL,7,FStevens said: "This is a significant
OL,8,Fmoment for Port Talbot and a major
OL,9,Fstep forward for the growing clean
OL,10,Fenergy industry in Wales. This
OL,11,Finvestment will further cement Port
OL,12,FTalbot as a hub of the industries of
OL,13,Fthe future, and heralds the next
OL,14,Fchapter of jobs, and investment to the
OL,15,Farea.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
