PN,46507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774576986
OL,3,CPort Talbot to become home of first
OL,4,Coffshore wind farm in Celtic Sea
OL,6,F"The UK Government has backed
OL,7,Fsteelworkers and the community in Port
OL,8,FTalbot with #100 million in direct
OL,9,Fsupport, and #500m for the
OL,10,Fconstruction of a new Electric Arc
OL,11,FFurnace ensuring that the town will
OL,12,Fmanufacture clean steel into the
OL,13,Ffuture.
OL,15,F"Thanks to our investment, the work of
OL,16,Ftrade unions and local businesses, and
OL,17,Fthe dedication and spirit of local
OL,18,Fpeople - Port Talbot and the whole
OL,19,Fregion have a very bright future."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@bO]
